data.description: Wonderful Colonial in the Putnam Valley school district offers a very private setting and features a formal living room with a wood-burning fireplace, a formal dining room, a family room, a powder room, and a dine-in kitchen with a slider out to a Trex deck, overlooking a pool with stone walls and Trex decking.  The second level offers a large primary suite with a balcony, sitting room/dressing room, a walk-in closet, and full bath with a jacuzzi tub, 2 additional large bedrooms, a hall bath, and laundry.  The lower level offers an additional 525 square feet and is great for an additional family room or guest area.  There are hardwood floors throughout the main and second floors, an updated powder room, large rooms, and more. Privacy galore!!
